snippet.title: Paw Paw Miaw (easy mode)
snippet.description:
This is a game that i sucked at as a little kid even on easy mode since the CPU is pretty brutal in all difficulties, but i managed to beat story mode one easy mode but i could not beat it in medium and hared mode.

I found this game in twplayergames.org, where the game was labeled as "Fighter Cats".

Surprisingly enough,  you can still play this game, because it's running through ruffle. https://www.twoplayergames.org/game/fighter-cats
